<p>Put this code into <code class="highlighter-rouge">Gemfile</code> and run <code class="highlighter-rouge">bundle install</code> :</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>gem 'jekyll-sitemap'
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>and add the following to <code class="highlighter-rouge">_config.yml</code></p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>gems:
 	 - jekyll-sitemap
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Donâ€™t forget to start server to see changes. :)</p>
